sub_title: Manager of International Strategy at Mobycon
summary: As an urban mobility specialist and as manager of international strategy, my work is focused on translating best practice in street design, traffic safety and urban mobility to suit cities and regions worldwide. My work includes training and capacity building, strategic projects and urban mobility plans in European and North-American contexts.
